{"tid":1472983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為我地既聲音太專注於連登，fb 同 IG呢3個平台。","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:42:57.000Z","uid":21562,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"89dba12caa6e350d15fe4c18ffbbdaf1b14fc525","tid":1472983,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:20:17.000Z","msg":"睇下香港地區youtube trending有幾多廢老片同下面幾多離地comment, 就知道香港有好大部分唔識用電話既廢人，而本身幫佢裝好埋個youtube app，基本上大部分既資訊都係黎自呢d中國式煽動既片。<br />\n<br />\n而問題就係外國人第一時間係youtube trending 睇到既就呢d片， 我地需要廣泛地係comment 度著手，揭露番個事實出黎。"},{"pid":"6961d54dd3d3f420992ef9e64760c4f5ee1f22e5","tid":1472983,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n816拎錢行動X英美港盟集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818民陣遊行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiENHnW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiENHnW.png&h=0871cd00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkRgLwS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkRgLwS.png&h=cee86880&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTN7R5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTN7R5o.jpg&h=b076ef80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd411c8228d58cf9ddcdca97145fbe34f5aea80f","tid":1472983,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"[公投] 係禁制令生效期間，我地全部人一齊做好文宣，再一次將所有訴求重現街頭，深入藍絲網絡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472512</a>"},{"pid":"030158bfbe12364cf675c1e22e405f512a0f364b","tid":1472983,"uid":165925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"突破盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好 聽日開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外跟手share下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vat3pSw.jpg\" d